'''''Star Wars Insider'' 54''' is the fifty-fourth issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was released to newsstands on [[June 14]], [[2001]]. This marked the final ''Star Wars Insider'' issue produced by [[Jeff Quick]], who had assumed chief editorial duties of the magazine with [[Star Wars Insider 52|issue 52]] upon [[Wizards of the Coast]] becoming the new publisher of ''Star Wars Insider''.

Issue 54 featured a special flip cover on the back of the magazine with related content celebrating the twentieth anniversary of the [[W:c:indianajones:Indiana Jones (franchise)|''Indiana Jones'']] film [[W:c:indianajones:Raiders of the Lost Ark|''Raiders of the Lost Ark'']]. Issue 54 also came packaged with a special [[LucasArts]] preview CD, while the newsstand version was available in an exclusive polybag. ''Star Wars Insider'' transitioned to square-bound binding with issue 54, in which the issue number is readable on the magazine's spine.

==Contents==
*"''Raiders of the Lost Ark'' 20th Anniversary Special"
*"[[Pernilla August: Mother of the Force]]" {{C|by [[Scott Chernoff]]}}
*:<small>One of Sweden's most celebrated actresses returns to the role that made her famous across the world.</small>
*"[[Peter Walpole: Ready, Set... Go!]]" {{C|by Scott Chernoff, [[Patrice Girod]], [[Brian Robb]], [[Oliver Denker]] and [[Stephen J. Sansweet|Stephen Sansweet]]}}
*:<small>Feng Shui is only the beginning.</small>
*"[[Ben Burtt: The Sound & the Vision]]" {{C|by Scott Chernoff}}
*:<small>He began as sound editor of a little-known production helmed by an unknown maverick writer/director. Today he's film editor of the most anticipated movie of the 21st Century.</small>

